archimate:BusinessObject.name: Data Model
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
A collection of entities, their properties and the relationships among them, which aims at formally representing a domain, a concept or a real-world thing.
Source: ISA2 - SEMIC Action https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/sites/default/files/methodology_and_tools_for_metadata_governance_and_management_for_eu_institutions.pdf
